BTC Price Direction Project

I am doing a Master's Final Work which consists of making an ML model which predicts BTC's price direction. 
My idea is using daily data (OHLCV, Macro and On-chain) to feed the models. 
The retrieved data is then preprocessed and engineered using Financial Machine Learning methodologies. 
Finally, a Kolmogorov Arnold Network is developed to predict price predictions and compared against benchmarks.
